---- MODULE SchemaAnalysis ----
\* Schema file analysis lifecycle. A schema is loaded from disk, parsed into IR, and validated.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Unloaded, Parsing, Parsed, AnalysisFailed

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, type_count, error_message

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Unloaded, Parsing, Parsed, AnalysisFailed}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Unloaded
    /\ type_count = 0
    /\ error_message = "none"

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Unloaded -> Parsing (analyze_file)
analyze_file ==
    /\ state = Unloaded
    /\ state' = Parsing
    /\ UNCHANGED <<type_count, error_message>>

\* Transition: Parsing -> Parsed (parse_succeeds)
parse_succeeds ==
    /\ state = Parsing
    /\ state' = Parsed
    /\ type_count := type_count + 1
    /\ UNCHANGED <<type_count, error_message>>

\* Transition: Parsing -> AnalysisFailed (parse_fails)
parse_fails ==
    /\ state = Parsing
    /\ state' = AnalysisFailed
    /\ error_message := "parse error"
    /\ UNCHANGED <<type_count, error_message>>

\* Transition: Parsed -> Unloaded (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = Parsed
    /\ state' = Unloaded
    /\ type_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED <<type_count, error_message>>

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ analyze_file
    \/ parse_succeeds
    \/ parse_fails
    \/ reset

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, type_count, error_message>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: SquisherInvariant (safety)
SquisherInvariant == []([](CompatibilityCheck = Incompatible => loss_count >= 0))

\* Property: ConcrodeImpliesNoLoss (safety)
ConcrodeImpliesNoLoss == []([](CompatibilityCheck = Concorde => loss_count = 0))

\* Property: AnalysisEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
AnalysisEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(SchemaAnalysis = Parsed \/ SchemaAnalysis = AnalysisFailed))


====
